{"tid":2298753,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"125宗確診> HIV愛滋病病毒 >2020年第三季","createTime":"2020-11-24T09:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T16:24:22.000Z","uid":311499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8804f2b64f7f74472cd62a648e7305327bcb2cbf","tid":2298753,"uid":311499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />96名男性，29名女性。53人 (同性或雙性接觸)、34人(異性接觸)、38人(不確定)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n       衞生署衞生防護中心於二○二○年第三季接獲125宗感染人類免疫力缺乏病毒（愛滋病病毒）的新增個案。自一九八四年以來，愛滋病病毒感染呈報個案累積至10 675宗。<br />\n<br />\n　　該季的125宗愛滋病病毒感染新增個案涉及96名男性及29名女性。其中，53人透過同性或雙性性接觸受感染，34人透過異性性接觸受感染，而餘下38宗個案的傳播途徑因呈報時資料不足而暫時未能確定。<br />\n<br />\n　　此外，季內錄得32宗愛滋病新增個案呈報，其中16宗（50%）透過同性或雙性性接觸受感染，13宗（41%）透過異性性接觸受感染，而餘下三宗個案（9%）的傳播途徑因呈報時資料不足而暫時未能確定。自一九八五年以來，本港愛滋病確診呈報個案累積有2 208宗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwpJyOp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwpJyOp.jpg&h=e656494b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d68cc153118f30bf2a3fe9ec6ac17144c24c336","tid":2298753,"uid":364115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1d5425fadd4c7c1b1431832a8a2407d8fc043c","tid":2298753,"uid":108158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"死基佬屌屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77f50fde812877195ff008c4428b7c883ea2353","tid":2298753,"uid":311499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7a1d5425fadd4c7c1b1431832a8a2407d8fc043c","tid":2298753,"uid":108158,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"死基佬屌屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a